erral of degrees your row will be asked to stand and file towards the stage entrance when you walk onto the stage you will give your name card to associate dean eamonn callan who will announce your name and dissertation title for doctoral students doctoral students will be hooded by their advisor and master's students by their program director please remember to unbutton your hoods before getting on stage dean steele will hand you your diploma and you will exit the stage and return to your seat reception warm hors d oeuvres champagne and non alcoholic beverages will be served immediately following the ceremony in the oak grove behind the seating area some tips to make the ceremony more enjoyable dress comfortably under your gown and for the heat sun block is recommended comfortable close toed shoes are recommended for walking across campus and in the oak grove there is debris from the trees in the diploma ceremony site we recommend that graduates eat a hearty breakfast your line up leader will have some snacks for you a champagne and hors d oeuvres reception will follow the suse ceremony at 2 00 pm water will be available at both ceremony locations plan to be at the suse ceremony by 12 00 pm on sunday walk by the locations of the suse and university ceremonies a few days before commencement weekend in order to plan how you will get there and where you will park you may want to drop off your guests before parking just in case you do not find parking close to the site commencement important information for graduating students guest information faculty information day of information for graduates speaker information june 17 2012 8 00am stanford stadium gates open for guests 8 45am all degree candidates who wish to participate in the stanford commencement ceremony arrive to the stadium in cap and gown 9 30am commencement procession begins 10 00am stanford commencement ceremony 11 00am suse ceremony setup in west oval grove 12 00pm all degree candidates who wish to participate in the suse diploma ceremony arrive to the west oval grove in cap and gown 12 30pm suse diploma ceremony 2 00pm reception in west oval grove stanford university school of education 485 lasuen mall stanford ca 94305 3096 tel 650 723 2109 copyright 2012 stanford university all rights reserved terms of use copyright complaints site map contact us helpsu suse it axess academic calendar stanford bulletin office of the registrar edmail stanfordwho stanfordyou login connect with us on facebook connect with us on twitter connect with us on youtube connect with us on flickr make a gift now
